flowchart TD
  Signal --> Assess{User harm active?}
  Assess -- Yes --> PauseRelease --> Mitigate{Remote mitigation available?}
  Mitigate -- Yes --> KillSwitch[Disable affected capability]
  Mitigate -- No --> Hotfix
  Assess -- No --> Observe
  KillSwitch --> Validate --> Communicate
  Hotfix --> Validate
